Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個機體是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑一架機體就具有匹敵聯結機的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是聯結機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 連同伴機都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣的話 噪音介入系統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強制解除聯結的解釋就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒有確鑿的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 不能使用聯結機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就沒有勝算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由 幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢恬不知恥的出現啊 我要為野牛報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 塔基姆 聽聽雛怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 聯結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和他打只有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是艾維拉小姐說有電波干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有試 怎麼知道不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不知道這是白費力氣嗎 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 他的行動突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 但這是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看來到了極限時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上重新啟動 不要設定極限時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不這麼做的話 對大腦的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一點都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是系統是一流的 如果部件是二流的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法完全發揮機能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為駕駛員這個部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了 渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那種事可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是現在這種的座艙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追加系統 理論上是可能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻像是走鋼絲般危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這就可以解釋發生電波干擾的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前給你看過的計劃 說不定可以實現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能追加上系統的時間是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒有其他選項了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的戰鬥是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統的構築完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機由我們這邊指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副長也問了同樣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看 公主殿下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 掩護那女孩是艦長的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個一個都讓我這麼火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你又要說試試看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞砸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡乖乖待著 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了青葉之後 我會好好和你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立模式 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接 LUXON
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯結機的系統內製造虛擬人格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過與其建立假想鏈接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令單獨聯結成為可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此短的時間裡構築出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是匆忙趕製的 和本來的使用方式也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對駕駛員的負擔也會很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用很短一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聯結是為了同調兩個駕駛員的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將思考數據以素粒子等級 傳送至1納秒後的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨的聯結 因為是和自己自身進行聯結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要接受信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 多餘的傳送數據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從傳送數據被接受來看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入聯結系統的噪音 那就是電波干擾的正體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算構築了系統 機體性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能放出同樣的噪音 就能抵消電波干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立模式 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能不如艾維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 只要我有部件的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優秀的部件！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人進行聯結？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉君和雛·里亞讚的emphatier波形驚人的一致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在系統上 也可以被認同為同一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以讓迪奧進行聯結的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是未知領域 不做做看的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吞沒了 我的思考數據…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的聯結實驗 只有雛一個人穿越了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初在聯合…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個循環…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛 是你吧 坐在那個上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們全殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾弗格尼·克達爾 立刻停止戰鬥行為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將對閣下以國家內亂罪予以逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暴力奪取的政權毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對行政局的殘暴抱持不滿的同志非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著你上宇宙的期間 事情比想像中進展的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊阿拉斯加基地做的太過火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被害影像成為了導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己給自己挖了墳墓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元臨時最高會議議長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向全軍播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個戰場由我來支配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來支配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的復仇還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續了70年的 我的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣捏碎你吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你乖乖躺在我下面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我有一點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看著雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你想要保護的東西 是自己的自尊和自我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我 我們有想要保護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要毀滅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方攻擊衛星出現高熱能反應 現在仍在增大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把衛星上儲存的3年份的nectoribium一口氣解放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種份量的能量 這顆衛星也不可能承受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 我可不是可以死在這種地方的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭腦 我的研究怎麼能在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算破壞沒法衛星也沒關係 只要能錯開射線就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NECTTAR屏障？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人攻擊目標計算出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐基利亞共和國 甘多 木倫陶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合加盟國 澳大利亞的加爾哥尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…三個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼連自己的國家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是所有世界上為數不多的nectoribium出產地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是對據說有數十年份的nectoribium
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用巨大NECTTAR炮擊中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引發大規模的誘爆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會毀滅…吧 地球它…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓那種事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們直接把它打掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到衛星的距離…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結機的話說不定趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不試試可不知道 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 停止那個才是首先要幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇拉小姐 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉他們跳躍了時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結系統 為了不讓思考出現時滯進行同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以素粒子等級 將信號傳遞到1納秒後的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們的思考同步到不需要的程度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把信號從0秒傳遞到0秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為了補完傳遞到1納秒後的未來這個現象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把接受者和接收機送往過去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事是真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊 但是只有這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如說那是真的 青葉他們為了回過去1納秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳100萬次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動距離繼續增大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標 E7—R1出現特異點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會被吸進去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BRADYON已經到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追的話 我們去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 弗洛姆 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 你也看到 所以應該知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要這樣回到過去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 做夢也沒有想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能在70年後的未來 交到摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向大家問好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我一直以來受大家關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話 自己說去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經沒有那個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 突然出現 把我們搞得很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUXON NEXT以及KARURA 信號消失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點就趕不上下一堂課了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里見過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雛 這是在搭訕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們是第一次見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫渡瀨青葉 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓…弓原雛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:49.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:49.23,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的呼應 響應的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:57.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:57.88,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的理由 請暫且忘記 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:07.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:07.08,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深知你 我在一直尋找著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:15.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:15.80,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕吻向那已飄渺的光的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:24.81,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:24.81,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}你那稍稍的猶豫不決 成為了那連接希望的蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:33.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:33.52,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}你那微微的彷徨 拉近了與那溫柔黎明的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:42.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:42.56,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}想去拯救 想去保護 那早已歸還於天空的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:49.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:49.44,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步 那已經早已傳達過夢想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:58.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:58.86,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能與我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的愛